The paper deals with understanding discourse relations among scenes in a video, which involves tasks such as scene identification, discourse parsing, and visual storytelling. These tasks are closely related to computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
